cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software or its results, please cite the paper below."
title: "Cross-Traffic Caching: a controlled evaluation harness for vehicular edge caching"
abstract: >-
  Open replay harness and cache-replacement policy implementations
  (including the SpatialUrgencyCache/SU policy and the tuning-free
  ExpectedDemandCache/EDC) for a controlled cross-traffic evaluation of
  vehicular edge caching across synthetic, SUMO, and real NGSIM traffic tiers.
type: software
